 Queensryche - A Measure of Success (1984)
From the tour of Queensryche's first album, The Warning, this is a show at Harpos, Detroit and also includes songs like the fabulous Queen Of The Reich from their first EP .
All in all around eighty minutes of music with great sonic quality if we remember it's a recording that was done 25 years ago.




Sound Quality: 9.5
